<h1>COMMISSIONS</h1>
<p>Status: OPEN</p>

<h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
<p>Please read the three slides carefully before submitting a commission form. By submitting a form you agree to have read and understand all of these terms.</p>

<li>I will email you if I have accepted the commission and we will discuss payment through email.</li>
<li>I reserve the right to reject a commission without reason.</li>
<li>Commissions will not start until full payment has been received. </li>
<li>Payment currency: USD</li>
<li>Refunds are allowed only if commission has not been started.</li>
<li>Commissions are for personal use only.</li>
<li>If you have any further questions please contact me via my contact page.</li>

<div id="commissionalert">
    {{#if success_msg}}
        <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
        {{success_msg}}
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        </div>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if error_msg}}
        <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
        {{error_msg}}
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        </div>
    {{/if}}
</div>

<div id="commission">
    <h2>Commission Form: </h2>
    <form action="" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="description">Description: </label>
            <textarea class="form-control" name="description" id="description" placeholder="Enter description of what you want for your commission" rows="3"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="url">Image reference: </label>
          <input
            type="url"
            id="url"
            name="url"
            class="form-control"
            placeholder="Enter url of image reference"
          />
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark btn-block">Submit</button>
    </form>
</div>
